        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-04-13T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-04-13T13:00:00-05:00" n="698" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d698">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/4–1246: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Embassy in China</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-04-13T13:00:00-05:00">April 13, 1946—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>643. Decision on deferment for exchange of letters and publicity on Eximbank
                    credit as recommended your 670, Apr 12, 6 p.m., taken prior to departure of
                    General Marshall yesterday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
